Description:
  A Yeoman generator for Bespoke.js presentations

Example:
  yo bespoke

  This will create:
    ├── .editorconfig                 : Config for editor like VIM...
    ├── .gitignore                    : Classic gitignore
    ├── gulpfile.js                   : Gulp build setup
    ├── package.json                  : You know for Node...
    ├── README.adoc                   : "How to" documentation
    ├── node_modules/**               : All the installed modules
    └── src
        ├── images
        │   └── bespoke-logo.jpg      : Example image
        ├── index.(pug | adoc | html) : Reference template
        ├── scripts
        │   └── main.js               : Bespoke setup with enabled plugins
        └── styles
            └── main.styl             : Reference stylesheet
